"A buffer distance has to be an **integer** or **floating point** value."
msgstr ""
"Una distanza di buffer deve essere un numero **intero** o **a virgola "
"mobile**."

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/vector_spatial_analysis_buffers.rst:217
